{"tid":2456111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"緬甸獨裁軍政府強徵附近民眾拆除沙袋及路障 影片顯示有人無力跪爬","createTime":"2021-03-21T15:58:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T16:48:45.000Z","uid":391580,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cc105be86a6f1f0ebb10966360d052b22062b64f","tid":2456111,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T15:58:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ygj2UfC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fygj2UfC.jpg&h=07322243&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3 月 18 日，在仰光瑪仰公鎮（Mayangon）與南奧卡拉帕鎮（South Okkalapa）的街道上，民眾被軍方強迫拆除沙袋與路障；仰光郊區亦有民眾遭到維安部隊毆打，在槍口的脅迫被拉伕加入。<br />\n<br />\n仰光達威鎮（Tamwe）民眾在 19 日拍攝到，軍人對被迫勞役扛沙袋的民眾拳打腳踢，受害者疑似無力繼續扛沙袋，在地上跪爬。<br />\n<br />\n過去軍政府時期，軍人強迫民眾鋪路、砍樹和粉刷牆壁；脅迫穆斯、基督徒與天主教徒在宗教節日，參與勞役以打壓佛教以外的宗教；強迫居民搬遷房屋以拓寬道路；強迫民眾搬遷至仰光周圍的新市鎮；強迫搬運工攜帶彈藥和糧食，以供應緬甸國軍在少數民族地區的戰爭；而囚犯被帶到游擊戰前線，當砲灰而被殺。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E7%94%9F%E8%80%85-%E7%95%B6%E8%BB%8D%E9%9A%8A%E6%88%90%E7%82%BA%E7%9B%9C%E5%8C%AA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%2580%2585-%25E7%2595%25B6%25E8%25BB%258D%25E9%259A%258A%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%259B%259C%25E5%258C%25AA%2F&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbUPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=09e59905\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%2580%2585-%25E7%2595%25B6%25E8%25BB%258D%25E9%259A%258A%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%259B%259C%25E5%258C%25AA%2F&h=8e13181d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E7%94%9F%E8%80%85-%E7%95%B6%E8%BB%8D%E9%9A%8A%E6%88%90%E7%82%BA%E7%9B%9C%E5%8C%AA/</a>"},{"pid":"9ee054df7e36286a2b426fc3ecfa1ad28c9179be","tid":2456111,"uid":167597,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:02:37.000Z","msg":"軍隊有無家人？<br />\n搵哂佢哋出來，睇下佢哋投唔投降"},{"pid":"8fd0ebd45b4a7f2705a766bfc4c2948175